<h2 class="contentH1">About Medix College Scarborough</h2>

<p class="contentp"><br />
    For over 40 years, Medix College has specialized in training students for careers in healthcare. Medix College Scarborough campus was established in 1999, and has become a respected institution in the community, including being awarded a seat on the board of the Scarborough Centre for Healthy Communities. The campus boasts modern facilities, fully equipped with the latest technology to provide an excellent learning and teaching environment.
    <br /><br />
    Medix College Scarborough Campus is situation on Lawrence Avenue East, between the Lawrence subway station and the Lawrence LRT station, which makes it a convenient commute for students in both the Toronto and Scarborough areas. We also have students from Pickering, Ajax, Markham and Richmond Hill, just to name a few.
    <br /><br />
    Medix College Scarborough Campus graduates consistently experience success in the current job market with the support of our committed Career Services Department. We nurture and maintain strong relationships with the Scarborough community and with employers all across the Greater Toronto Area (GTA), all of whom contribute to our exceptionally high employment success rate.
</p>
